  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I did that, together with other carpentry or cabinet-making work in the shop.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Most of the rest of the people worked in the enamel works.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And at the same time, Oskar Schindler, according to this plan that he, at one time, delivered to the German authorities, he began to build a new building in which he was going to build these new cartridges for the-- for rockets for the German [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Army industry or whatever.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So from 1943 on, we-- we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes in-- in 1944-- and possibly this was already the-- the-- end of-- or no, I'm sorry, the middle of 1944.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But before that in-- when I worked in the-- the enamel works factory together with this fellow Wuczek, on occasion this fellow Wuczek would instruct me as a boss.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He had the perfect right to instruct me to do whatever he wanted me to do.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on-- on one of those requests that he had for me is that I steal pots and pans and-- and lower them on a rope to him on the outside of the factory, where he would be able to pick them up at night and take them away into the city of Krakow.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, as a prisoner of that camp itself, I had no benefit from it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was no-- nothing that I would have gotten paid or received for it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I simply had to follow the order of my boss.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so I wound up stealing pots and pans from Oskar Schindler's factory for this fellow Wuczek.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he did not need to threaten me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was an order-- a request from a non-Jew to a Jew inside of a camp was sufficient to get me to do what he wanted to do.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
